<HL>
   Pier 1 Imports Inc. Sales Rise
</HL>
<DATE>
04/19/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   PIR
</CO>
<LP>
   FORT WORTH, Texas -- Pier 1 Imports Inc. said March sales
increased 23% to $48 million from $38.9 million a year ago.
   The specialty retailer said sales rose 6.4% at stores open
for more than a year.
